",\"Name\":\"МП-34\"},\"Room\":{\"Code\":68,\"Name\":\"4214\"}}],\"Semestr\":\"Осенний семестр 2016-2017 г. \"}";
    private static final Gson gson = new Gson();
    private static ScheduleApiResponseInternal responseInternal
            = gson.fromJson(VALID_JSON, ScheduleApiResponseInternal.class);

    private Set<ScheduleItem> adapted = ResponseAdapter.adapt(responseInternal);

    @Test
    public void thereAre2LessonsOnFirstSaturday(){
        int cnt = 0;

        for(ScheduleItem scheduleItem : adapted) {
            if (scheduleItem.getDayOfWeek() == Calendar.SATURDAY
                    && scheduleItem.repeatsEveryFirstWeekOfMonth())
                cnt++;
        }

        assertEquals(2, cnt);
    }

    @Test
    public void thereIsEconomicsLectureOnFirstAndThirdWeekFriday(){
        boolean found = false;

        for (ScheduleItem scheduleItem : adapted) {
            if (scheduleItem.getDayOfWeek() == Calendar.FRIDAY
                    && scheduleItem.repeatsEveryFirstWeekOfMonth()
                    && scheduleItem.repeatsEveryThirdWeekOfMonth()
                    && scheduleItem.isLecture()
                    && scheduleItem.getDisciplineName().contains("Экономическая")){
                found = true;
            }
        }

        assertTrue(found);
    }

    @Test
    public void thereIsAlwaysAllDayMilitaryLessonsOnMonday(){
        int cnt = 0;
        for (ScheduleItem scheduleItem : adapted) {
            if (scheduleItem.isMilitaryLesson()
                    && scheduleItem.repeatsEveryFirstWeekOfMonth()
                    && scheduleItem.repeatsEverySecondWeekOfMonth()
                    && scheduleItem.repeatsEveryThirdWeekOfMonth()
                    && scheduleItem.repeatsEveryThirdWeekOfMonth()
                    && scheduleItem.getDayOfWeek() == Calendar.MONDAY) {
                cnt++;
            }
        }

        assertEquals(7, cnt);
    }


